     H            Y.
      ** UTLR58 *************************************************
      *  RETRIEVE CONTACT NAME FOR CUSTOMER                     *
      *                                                         *
      ***********************************************************
      *  CALLING SEQ.
      *                    CALL 'UTLR58'
      *                    PARM           $NONY      4
      *                    PARM           $USRID    10
      *                    PARM           $USRNM    30
      *   IN  $NONY     4A        DELIVERY CODE
      *   OUT $USRID   10A        IAF USER ID
      *   OUT $USRNM   30A        IAF CONTACT NAME
      ***********************************************************
     FAB#PLY9 IF  E           K        DISK
      ***********************************************************
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *==================================================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $USRID 10
     C                     PARM           $USRNM 30
      ****************************************************
      * MAIN ROUTINE
      ****************************************************
      *
     C           $NONY     IFNE *BLANKS
      *
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     NONY    40
     C           NONY      CHAINAB#PLY9              51
     C           *IN51     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELUAUSER    $USRID
     C                     CALL 'UTLC58'
     C                     PARM           $USRID
     C                     PARM           $USRNM
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   $USRID
     C                     MOVEL'PC COORD'$USRNM
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *
